#rad
       cos(α+2kπ)=cos α
               |    π
cos(π-α)=-cos α|cos(-- +α)=-sin α
               |    2
---------------|-------------------
               |    π
cos(π+α)=-cos α|cos(-- -α)=sin α
               |    2
#deg
        cos(α+k*360°)=cos α
cos(180°-α)=-cos α|cos(90°+α)=-sin α
------------------|-------------------
cos(180°+α)=-cos α|cos(90°-α)=sin α